### ESPN Scoreboard — Men's, First Four (March 19)
# groups=50 filters to NCAA Men's Tournament events only.
# Used by importResults() and discoverTournamentId().
# Look for: events[].id (ESPN event ID), events[].competitions[].tournament.id (tournament ID),
#           events[].competitions[].competitors[].{team.id, winner}

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/mens-college-basketball/scoreboard?groups=50&limit=100&dates={{date_first_four}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ESPN Scoreboard — Women's, First Four (March 19)
# groups=49 filters to NCAA Women's Tournament events only.

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/womens-college-basketball/scoreboard?groups=49&limit=100&dates={{date_first_four}}
Accept: application/json

